snippet.title: JankBrain - Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
JankBrain wants to take over the world! Inspired by 16 bit run and gun platformers of the 90s, JankBrain must tackle 55 challenging levels including mine cart, rocket pack, and boss battles. Discover secret levels and compete for speedrun medals as you play! Launching January 2021 on PS4.

http://loggames.ca
